CHOCTAW AND CHICKASAW NATIONS v. Kay KIMBELL. No. 4658. United States Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Dec. 7, 1953. W. F. Semple, Tulsa, Okl., and Lynn Adams, Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant's.’ _ C. B. Cochran, Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and BRATTON and PICKETT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on appellants’ motion.
